/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: JBPM4_TASK */
/*==============================================================*/
create table JBPM4_TASK
(
DBID_ bigint not null,
CLASS_ char(1) not null,
DBVERSION_ integer not null,
NAME_ varchar(255),
DESCR_ longtext,
STATE_ varchar(255),
SUSPHISTSTATE_ varchar(255),
ASSIGNEE_ varchar(255),
FORM_ varchar(255),
PRIORITY_ integer,
CREATE_ datetime,
DUEDATE_ datetime,
PROGRESS_ integer,
SIGNALLING_ bit,
EXECUTION_ID_ varchar(255),
ACTIVITY_NAME_ varchar(255),
HASVARS_ bit,
SUPERTASK_ bigint,
EXECUTION_ bigint,
PROCINST_ bigint,
SWIMLANE_ bigint,
TASKDEFNAME_ varchar(255),
INDEX FK_TASK_SUPERTASK (SUPERTASK_),
primary key (DBID_)
)
type=InnoDB;

alter table JBPM4_TASK comment '任务表
';
